query:
UPDATE teams
               SET name = $2, identifier = $3, icon = $4, color = $5, updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         name,
                         identifier,
                         icon,
                         color,
                         created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
